reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 18, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good quality for money
reviews.reviewText: II bought these for my M4600 Laptop HDD installment, but the 3x6mm H nuts in this kit have a little too big of head size and they did not fit in my laptop. But the overall quality of nuts was very good and material used was definitely a good grade alloy. For this price I believe the number of screws and nuts I received in a nice box was worth it !

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 8, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Everything I needed.
reviews.reviewText: I recently spent a lot of money on a new computer build. The Motherboard manufacturer did not include screws. The case manufacturer did not include any screws. This set had everything I needed to start and finish the build and was very well organized.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 18, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Yes indeed it came in handy.. Only caveat would be that more of the screws were black anodized color Im good with it.. Recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good value for product
reviews.reviewText: I have, so far, used this to put in a motherboard and assemble components into a used case. I have used many of the screws, but not all, and the only thing I have found so far that did not work as expected was the bolt holes for the PCI slots. Nothing fit quite correctly into those, but that may also be the case. It isn't a stellar product, but the screws seem to fit and work as intended. The base nuts intended to be inserted into the case to support the motherboard fit the intended screws well, and those screws also fit the nuts already in the case. I would recommend this product.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 25, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great value for so many accessories!
reviews.reviewText: Love that it comes with its own case and includes a sticker guide for the components. The small screws are great for a spare side-panel thumb screw (which is smaller than traditional thumbscrews). Love that it also comes with the perfect small size side panel thumb screw insert. Size makes it easy to transport, and case is durable.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Important if you fix or build computers
reviews.reviewText: You are always missing something, a stand off or screw. This fixes that problem.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Exactly as described
reviews.reviewText: Enough fasteners to complete about five full desktop builds. All of the parts are well machined with no obvious flaws or burrs. The metal must be fairly hard because after using about a quarter of them I never noticed a single scratch or stripping on the heads.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 18, 2021
reviews.reviewText: many of these fasteners are hard to come by. very happy to find this, can be a lifesaver, includes a big supply of each type.
